data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of historic Haymount, Fayetteville, NC! This charming residence boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, providing the perfect blend of modern comfort and classic elegance. Step inside to discover a recently updated interior featuring top-notch finishes. The kitchen is a chef's delight with sleek quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, and stylish laminate flooring that adds a touch of contemporary flair. Unwind in the primary suite, complete with a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. A second fireplace graces the living space, ensuring comfort and charm throughout the home. Experience the beauty of Carolina seasons from the front porch, where you can soak in the neighborhood vibes, or retreat to the back deck and screened-in porch for a more private outdoor oasis. With ample storage space, this home is designed to accommodate your every need. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Haymount gem your own!
